*apcupsd-3.10.5-r1 (26 Feb 2003)

  26 Feb 2003; Zach Welch <zwelch@gentoo.org> apcupsd-3.10.5-r1.ebuild,
  files/3.10.5/apache.conf, files/3.10.5/init.patch,
